 />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"遮住左睇唔到..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"2:43 突o左少少出黎 似係震臂"},{"pid":"4cd42dbb1c33944f56f9fe0b46a0e290a2025595","tid":934780,"uid":76419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gX6CEjiR8e8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgX6CEjiR8e8&d=zI4jTfJbMFlomC76MbivgNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2fa8703b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gX6CEjiR8e8</a><br />\n一開頭 GG用支爛木結他撚9班人 件t shirt又玩鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031c9c6c50a7cd80df38bf6f8829866549f38d57","tid":934780,"uid":76419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.musicradar.com/news/guthrie-govan-the-older-wiser-player-knows-in-a-deep-intuitive-way-that-its-the-quality-of-the-playing-that-counts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.musicradar.com%2Fnews%2Fguthrie-govan-the-older-wiser-player-knows-in-a-deep-intuitive-way-that-its-the-quality-of-the-playing-that-counts&d=zI4jTfJbMFlomC76MbivgNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=749faa15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.musicradar.com/news/guthrie-govan-the-older-wiser-player-knows-in-a-deep-intuitive-way-that-its-the-quality-of-the-playing-that-counts</a><br />\n<br />\nGG又訓話<br />\n<br />\n//<strong>I&rsquo;d have to go back to the woodshed to learn how to get a decent A chord out of a Tele</strong>//<br />\n<br />\n//&ldquo;I think if I had one guitar and I had to do everything I do on that one guitar, and that guitar was, say, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>a '50s Tele</strong></span>, I would have issues. So, yes, there are many things I do that a Tele of that era doesn&rsquo;t allow me to do. But I&rsquo;m fortunate now that I have more than one guitar and I look to each of them to do different things.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;But when people talk about technique they often talk about how many notes a second you can play or how evenly you can pick. But another part of technique is, do you know how to get the most out of this instrument?<span style=\"color: red;\"> Do you know the recorded lineage of it? Do you know what a great Tele sound or 335 sound should be? That in itself is something you can spend years on, knowing where each one of those classic tones fits. Although I&rsquo;m fairly comfortable with Strats now, but I&rsquo;d have to go back to the woodshed to learn how to get a decent A chord out of a Tele.</span>&rdquo;//"},{"pid":"8df7e235371dfc7dcfdc119dc36272b33187b097","tid":934780,"uid":48065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"連登好少人講Guthrie <br />\n<br />\n佢係我男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n公仔面頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9b3604bbc6749f0ee5172cff2b2bf9ca6b01e3","tid":934780,"uid":48065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bUZK9dasP8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbUZK9dasP8s&d=zI4jTfJbMFlomC76MbivgNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8eec3bf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bUZK9dasP8s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚正"},{"pid":"6e39ab3b582e39da6bc57242d38b15dd7f1e2a60","tid":934780,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"條條都咁撚正<br />\n玩odd times對佢黎講同4/4無分別"}]}